                        <interp inst="t18230409-58-person603" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     </persName>
                   and others being therein), and stealing seven handkerchiefs, value 2 s.; two yards of stuff, value 2 s.; a shift, value 1 s.; a table-cloth, value 1 s.; a pair of stockings, value 3 d.; a waistcoat, value 6 d.; a hat, value 5 s., and two coats, value 1 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18230409-58-victim605" type="victimName">
