                     <interp inst="t18230409-58-person607" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took him in charge and found a pair of stockings in his pocket.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 65.</p>
